Quick Start:

1. crate a conda env for freegsnke
conda create -n freegsnke python=3.10
conda activate freegsnke

2. clone and install
git clone https://github.com/sanabel18/freegs4e_v0.12.0_nchc.git
git clone https://github.com/sanabel18/freegsnke_v2.1.0_nchc.git

freegs4e_v0.12.0_nchc
pip install -e ".[dev]"

cd freegsnke_v2.1.0_nchc 
pip install -e ".[dev]"

in  this steps, if some packages is missing , just pip install them

3. try freegsnke_v2.1.0_nchc/examples/machine_first.py 
   or freegsnke_v2.1.0_nchc/examples/inverse_solve.py


